## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of social media's effects. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may include biases or incomplete data. Further research, including empirical studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms means that new effects and trends may emerge that are not covered in this report.